Anovuyo Cira's remains washed up in Kenton-on-Sea. eNCA’s Ronald Masinda is covering this story. #dstv403 KENTON-ON-SEA - The body of an 11-year-old boy who drowned on New Year’s Day has been found. Anovuyo Cira's remains washed up in Kenton-on-Sea. READ: Three children drown at Kenton-on-Sea He was with three other children when they were swept away. The three girls' bodies were recovered on 2 January.